Fri Jul 27 10:50:39 EDT 2001 Daniel Veillard <daniel@veillard.com>

	* libxslt/transform.[ch]: applied changes from Tom Moog #58002
	* libexslt/functions.c libxslt/documents.c libxslt/extensions.c:
